### eCast API Test Requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension

### ─── Health Check ───
GET http://localhost:8000/api/status HTTP/1.1

###

### ─── Upload ePub File ───
# Replace 'test.epub' with your actual file path
POST http://localhost:8000/api/upload HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.epub"
Content-Type: application/epub+zip

< ./uploads/test.epub
--boundary--

###

### ─── Get Chapters ───
# Replace {file_id} with the actual file ID from upload response
GET http://localhost:8000/api/chapters/abc12345 HTTP/1.1

###

### ─── Preview Chapter Text ───
GET http://localhost:8000/api/preview/abc12345/0 HTTP/1.1

###

### ─── Start Processing ───
POST http://localhost:8000/api/process?file_id=abc12345&chapters=0,1 HTTP/1.1

###

### ─── Check Progress (Polling) ───
GET http://localhost:8000/api/progress-poll/task1234 HTTP/1.1

###

### ─── Get Audio File ───
GET http://localhost:8000/api/audio/task1234/ar HTTP/1.1

###

### ─── Get Translated Texts ───
GET http://localhost:8000/api/text/task1234 HTTP/1.1

###

### ─── Download All as ZIP ───
GET http://localhost:8000/api/download/task1234 HTTP/1.1
